      "date": "2013-07-24 11:46:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/da083cd4-f44c-11e2-9221-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  2 tests failed: replay-single, sanity.",
